overview: A group film by students of the San Francisco Film Workshop, under the direction of Ronald Chase.  A boy tries to comfort a woman who has just been dumped, but balks when he learns about the circumstances of the relationship. Crew: Laura Byrne Vadim Oss Derek Dabkoski Max Strebel Scott Cowan Beni Strebel Max Sokoloff John Lucas
